Work Halted at AngloGold’s Mponeng Mine to Investigate Worker’s Death

-- B y   M k h u l u l i   M a n c o t y w a
-- 
2011-05-27T14:41:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/work-halted-at-anglogold-s-mponeng-mine-to-investigate-worker-s-death.html
Work was halted at  AngloGold Ashanti
Ltd. (ANG) ’s Mponeng mine in  South Africa  to investigate a death that
ocurred today at the mine, located in Carletonville, spokesman
 Alan Fine  said by phone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
